        {
            "title": "美股靠穩　道指升117點收市　納指升0.39%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數反覆靠穩，美國的貿易政策存在不確定。中概股彈1.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241219_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241219_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國聯邦巡迴上訴法院批准特朗普政府暫緩執行國際貿易法院，阻止政府對加徵關稅措施的裁決，恢復實施關稅政策。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數走勢反覆，高開91點後，最多升167點，但亦曾倒跌270點，低見41828點，收市報42215點，跌117點，跌幅0.28%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數初段曾升1.5%，收市升幅顯著收窄至0.39%，報19175點，升74點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數收報5912點，上升23點，升幅0.4%，曾升0.93%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數反彈1.44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大型科技股個別發展，當中Nvdia上季業績勝預期，股價一度炒高6.4%，收市仍漲3.3%；特斯拉(Tesla)及亞馬遜分別升0.4%及0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國商業軟件公司Salesforce業績優於預期，但未能消除市場對其業務放慢的憂慮，股價急滑3.3%，為表現最差道指成份股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">惠普(HP)及電子產品零售商百思買(Best Buy)因應美國關稅政策，齊削全年業績展望，股價分別插水8.3%及7.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14969473-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%9d%a0%e7%a9%a9%e3%80%80%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87117%e9%bb%9e%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e3%80%80%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%870-39",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1-704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-30 08:35:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股偏軟  先升後跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市偏軟。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市下滑0.19%，報547點，早段最多曾升0.53%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報8716點，跌9點，跌幅0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報7779點，跌8點，跌幅0.11%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報23933點，跌104點，跌幅0.44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報39982點，下挫0.36%或144點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報14116點，反彈0.11%或16點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普關稅被當地貿易法院法官叫停，消息利好股市，不過美國經濟數據疲弱抵消了關稅利好。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14969475-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e5%85%88%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-30 08:30:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美元指數失守100關口　下跌1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元結束兩日升勢，美元指數再失守100水平，較早時報99.339，下跌1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國經濟數據疲弱，上周新申領失業救濟人數多過預期，另外，美國上訴法院批准暫緩執行貿易法院命令，特朗普政府關稅政策仍然有效，都影響美元表現。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐元兌美元升0.73%，報1.1374美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元兌日圓下跌0.57%，報143.99日圓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元兌瑞郎下跌 0.59%，報0.822。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14969517-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88100%e9%97%9c%e5%8f%a3%e3%80%80%e4%b8%8b%e8%b7%8c1-2",
